author: ikneadyou Sports Massage
text: Really convenient. Buses 334, 335, 49, 98,187, 157, 198, 99 and 502 goes here. Not the biggest outlet but still well equipped. Downside, no shower. Food is abundant nearby.

author: Rayyan Irfan
text: A very vibrant gym. Even though I am AFBL. I felt warmth at thja gym. The Club BA Azri is very welcoming and helpful. He gives morale support to fitness goers at this gym.

author: Hamid Harron
text:
I’ve been going to AF Jurong for a while now, and it’s easily one of the best neighborhood gyms around. The equipment is well-maintained, the space is always clean, and the staff is super friendly and helpful. Whether you’re a beginner or an experienced lifter, there’s something for everyone here.

What really sets this gym apart is the community—everyone is supportive and motivated, making workouts so much more enjoyable. There’s never an issue with overcrowding, and the membership rates are very reasonable for the quality you get.

Highly recommend this place if you’re looking for a no-nonsense, well-equipped gym with a great atmosphere!

author: Jennifer Kee
text: The towels to wipe down equipment haven’t been changed or cleaned since they open a year ago…. Please change or get them washed at the very least, thank you.
